Package project_package

Class Project

java.lang.Object
project_package.Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Project extends Object implements Serializable
The Project class represents a project entity with its attributes and associated project teams. It implements Serializable for object serialization.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Robin Deplanques
